  AbilityName: Rock dash
  Description: "By paying a set number of coins, this character goes on a full-speed
    sprint\u2014as if launched from a cannon\u2014charging forward five spaces. Along
    the way, they steal 5 coins from every player caught in their path. Sticky traps
    and Star Spaces? No problem. They\u2019re completely skipped, because nothing
    stops this sprint."
